OL,3,CFather calls for more awareness about
OL,4,CFetal Alcohol Spectrum Disorder
OL,6,FA Jersey father is calling for more
OL,7,Finformed training, knowledge and
OL,8,Fsupport for children living with Fetal
OL,9,FAlcohol Spectrum Disorder - known as
OL,10,FFASD.
OL,12,FThe condition, which can be the result
OL,13,Fof an alcohol-exposed pregnancy,
OL,14,Faffects the central nervous system and
OL,15,Fbrain development.
OL,17,FAndrew Wright's adopted son, Rylie,
OL,18,F11, lives with the condition after
OL,19,Fbeing exposed to alcohol before birth.
