OL,3,CFather calls for more awareness about
OL,4,CFetal Alcohol Spectrum Disorder
OL,6,FHe explains: "I noticed something
OL,7,Fdifferent when Rylie started primary
OL,8,Fschool, where the environment became
OL,9,Fmore structured, and that's when I
OL,10,Fstarted asking questions about whether
OL,11,Fhe's autistic or whether he might have
OL,12,FADHD."
OL,14,FFASD is a lifelong neurodevelopmental
OL,15,Fdisability which affects the central
OL,16,Fnervous system and brain development.
OL,17,FThe condition can also impact the
OL,18,Fentire body, including internal and
OL,19,Fexternal organs.
