OL,3,CFather calls for more awareness about
OL,4,CFetal Alcohol Spectrum Disorder
OL,6,FAndrew believes the stigma and lack of
OL,7,Funderstanding about the disorder may
OL,8,Fprevent parents from seeking a
OL,9,Fdiagnosis for their child, describing
OL,10,Fit as "one of the biggest barriers".
OL,12,FHe continues: "Parents might feel that
OL,13,Fthey will be blamed or they will be
OL,14,Fheld responsible. They absolutely will
OL,15,Fnot".
OL,17,FAndrew adds that while some
OL,18,Fprofessionals may have heard of what
OL,19,FFASD is: "It doesn't mean they
OL,20,Fnecessarily understand the symptoms of
OL,21,Fthe condition or how it presents."
