OL,3,CFather calls for more awareness about
OL,4,CFetal Alcohol Spectrum Disorder
OL,6,FIt's estimated that one in thirteen
OL,7,Falcohol-exposed pregnancies can lead
OL,8,Fto FASD.
OL,10,FSandra Butcher, Chief Executive of the
OL,11,FNational Organisation for FASD,
OL,12,Fexplains: "People with FASD often have
OL,13,Ftrouble with how the brain processes
OL,14,Fincoming information and how the brain
OL,15,Fstores and retrieves that information.
OL,17,F"Somebody with FASD may struggle with
OL,18,Fabstract thinking or with impulse
OL,19,Fcontrol - especially if they get very
OL,20,Fanxious."
