OL,3,CFather calls for more awareness about
OL,4,CFetal Alcohol Spectrum Disorder
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the data on safe limits for
OL,7,Falcohol consumption during pregnancy
OL,8,Fremains unclear, with one expert
OL,9,Ftelling ITV that there isn't any "firm
OL,10,Fevidence".
OL,12,FDr. Jo Darwood, a GP at the Jersey
OL,13,FWomen's Health Hub, says: "All the
OL,14,Fguidance says at the moment is that we
OL,15,Fshould try and drink no alcohol in
OL,16,Fpregnancy - particularly in the first
OL,17,Fthree months."
OL,19,FBased on UK statistics, up to 7,000
OL,20,Fpeople could be living in Guernsey and
OL,21,FJersey with the condition.
